topPRs.body:
- Document TEXT_EMBEDDING model type in README
- Add embedding configuration parameters to README examples
- Update package.json agentConfig with embedding parameters
- Remove outdated note about embeddings not being implemented

> [!NOTE]
> Documents TEXT_EMBEDDING support and adds embedding model/dimension config parameters in README and agentConfig.
> 
> - **README**:
>   - Add `TEXT_EMBEDDING` as a provided model and describe configurable dimensions (256–3072).
>   - Include `OPENROUTER_EMBEDDING_MODEL` and `OPENROUTER_EMBEDDING_DIMENSIONS` in settings and `.env` examples, plus fallbacks `EMBEDDING_MODEL` and `EMBEDDING_DIMENSIONS`.
>   - Document new config options for embedding model and dimensions; remove outdated note about embeddings not implemented.
> - **package.json (agentConfig)**:
>   - Add parameters: `OPENROUTER_EMBEDDING_MODEL`, `EMBEDDING_MODEL`, `OPENROUTER_EMBEDDING_DIMENSIONS`, `EMBEDDING_DIMENSIONS` with defaults.
>
